260
00:22:26.510 --> 00:22:30.820
- And looking at it, it seems like money is on my side as well. 
 - I am a king.

261
00:22:30.820 --> 00:22:36.750
I'm a building owner. Would you care to see whether money or being a king is more powerful here?

262
00:22:36.750 --> 00:22:38.490
What?

263
00:22:42.040 --> 00:22:44.320
- Yoon So Ah.
- Yes?

264
00:22:44.320 --> 00:22:48.590
You forgot that the day after tomorrow you're supposed to work on the farm didn't you?

265
00:22:50.460 --> 00:22:52.710
I'm sorry.

266
00:22:52.710 --> 00:22:57.580
This makes it difficult for me. Being close is one thing but a contract is a contract.

267
00:22:57.580 --> 00:23:02.400
I'm sorry. Lately my mind has been scattered. You're going out in the afternoon, right? I'll go—

268
00:23:02.400 --> 00:23:04.550
Where are you going?

269
00:23:05.530 --> 00:23:09.880
I don't know what you want her to do but whatever it is, it's a no.

270
00:23:09.880 --> 00:23:14.330
Yoon So Ah is indebted to me. She incurred a cancellation fee when she broke her contract to sell me that land.

271
00:23:14.330 --> 00:23:19.470
She needs to earn money and pay back this debt to be done with this contract.

272
00:23:21.010 --> 00:23:22.880
I'll see you then.

273
00:23:32.080 --> 00:23:35.950
It's because you didn't let me sell that land.

274
00:23:40.600 --> 00:23:46.130
Give me some money. My servant owes a cancellation fee to that half-god half-human because she didn't sell him that land.

275
00:23:46.130 --> 00:23:49.000
Because we are the reason that she has that debt...

276
00:23:51.450 --> 00:23:53.680
Don't make me laugh.

277
00:23:56.780 --> 00:23:58.660
You look like you've just gotten a call from Ha Baek.

278
00:23:58.660 --> 00:24:02.110
CEO Sin is a pretty good player. He listens very well to his coach.

279
00:24:02.110 --> 00:24:06.030
That's a name I still don't want to hear. Don't say it if you can help it.

280
00:24:06.030 --> 00:24:10.420
No. I'm going to keep saying it until you get tired of it.

281
00:24:12.490 --> 00:24:15.450
Now what are you play-acting?

282
00:24:15.450 --> 00:24:19.520
I heard that it's women's romantic fantasy to be served breakfast by the man they love.

283
00:24:19.520 --> 00:24:24.090
- It's must be the romantic fantasy of foolish human women.
- Be a human woman just for a bit.

284
00:24:24.090 --> 00:24:26.780
Don't I need a man that I love to do that?

285
00:24:26.780 --> 00:24:30.650
How many steps do I have left? 50? 100?

286
00:24:32.680 --> 00:24:34.590
Will I be able to even reach you?

287
00:24:34.590 --> 00:24:38.760
- Get out. I need to shower.
- Alright.

288
00:24:47.910 --> 00:24:51.420
She's the most difficult woman in the world.

289
00:24:51.420 --> 00:24:53.840
I know that, I do.

290
00:25:01.610 --> 00:25:03.400
What's up?

291
00:25:04.470 --> 00:25:08.540
I can't today, my schedule is filled to the brim.

292
00:25:09.540 --> 00:25:11.490
I'll contact you.

293
00:25:15.080 --> 00:25:22.620
When I go back to the gods' realm I'm going to turn one of them into a mackerel and the other into a sparrow.

294
00:25:33.060 --> 00:25:35.150
<i>Yes, Lord Ha Baek.</i>

295
00:25:35.150 --> 00:25:37.850
Are you earning lots of money?

296
00:25:37.900 --> 00:25:44.300
<i>What? Yes. I have a lot of duck boat customers waiting. Ah, Lord Joo Dong called me.</i>

297
00:25:44.360 --> 00:25:47.040
What? Where is he? Why isn't he coming?

298
00:25:47.040 --> 00:25:51.010
<i>He said that he's coming soon and not to go anywhere and wait for him.</i>

299
00:25:51.010 --> 00:25:54.420
But why did he call you and not me?

300
00:25:54.420 --> 00:25:58.880
<i>Moo Ra told him not to call you because you keep asking for money.</i>

301
00:25:58.880 --> 00:26:00.890
How impertinent.

302
00:26:10.720 --> 00:26:15.860
<i>That person is apparently the person who saved me.</i>

303
00:26:15.860 --> 00:26:19.820
<i>That person. But...</i>

304
00:26:21.490 --> 00:26:26.110
<i>What? What else are you saying?</i>

305
00:26:33.860 --> 00:26:39.300
What is she saying? The part where she says that that person saved her is good

306
00:26:39.300 --> 00:26:46.560
"but,"  "but,"  but... That's the part that makes me uncomfortable.

307
00:26:49.040 --> 00:26:52.860
I'm a little late. The person who was supposed to take the shift after me at the convenience store was late.

308
00:26:52.860 --> 00:26:54.910
- Nam Soo Ri.
- Yes?

309
00:26:54.910 --> 00:26:58.320
It's always the same dream but I can't just ignore it.

310
00:26:58.320 --> 00:27:01.910
I can't hear the most important part.

311
00:27:03.460 --> 00:27:06.960
Is there no fix for this?

312
00:27:12.920 --> 00:27:17.230
Theres... there's nothing.

313
00:27:18.440 --> 00:27:20.310
Why?

314
00:27:30.200 --> 00:27:33.030
<i>- What is it? </i> 
- Is anything going on with you?

315
00:27:33.030 --> 00:27:37.110
What? Your tone makes it sound like there should be something going on with me.

316
00:27:37.110 --> 00:27:40.410
Your dating life has gone badly and now you're all twisted up.

317
00:27:40.410 --> 00:27:42.480
There's nothing wrong with my dating life.

318
00:27:42.480 --> 00:27:47.650
<i>Then the genetic material of your dating cells is abnormal. Does it make any sense to love so that you can break up?</i>

319
00:27:47.650 --> 00:27:52.720
I've heard of breaking up because you're in love but I've never heard of loving in order to break up.

320
00:27:52.720 --> 00:27:57.510
You left out 'well', to break up well.

321
00:27:59.370 --> 00:28:04.190
- I'm hanging up now.
- Is the boyfriend that saved you doing well?

322
00:28:07.990 --> 00:28:11.920
Is someone having a ridiculous relationship like that?

323
00:28:31.940 --> 00:28:35.080
You are trying really hard even though you know you can't do it.

324
00:28:35.080 --> 00:28:39.270
I heard that there's a thing called interest if you borrow money.

325
00:28:40.920 --> 00:28:45.130
When I go back to the Water Kingdom, I'll give you a lot.

326
00:28:45.130 --> 00:28:47.300
Why would I need money in the gods' realm?

327
00:28:47.300 --> 00:28:51.770
I'm not saying that I'd give you interest in the form of money. If you need anything, tell me.

328
00:28:51.770 --> 00:28:54.590
Would you give me your kingship?

329
00:28:56.500 --> 00:28:58.580
Of course something like that can't happen.

330
00:28:58.580 --> 00:29:03.000
No matter how much I pick on you, I don't want to see that kind of grief.

331
00:29:03.000 --> 00:29:07.810
- I want to see you for a long time.
- Can you really not do it?

332
00:29:07.810 --> 00:29:13.560
I could give you money or a diamond ring, but Moo Ra doesn't want me to.

333
00:29:13.560 --> 00:29:17.640
I'm the kind of man who listens to his woman.

334
00:29:17.640 --> 00:29:22.920
I saw this on the internet. They call that kind of thing "being whipped".

335
00:29:22.920 --> 00:29:27.420
I like "being whipped".

336
00:29:29.620 --> 00:29:33.320
- I'm leaving.
- Wait.

337
00:29:34.220 --> 00:29:37.190
- I have some business with you too.
- What?

338
00:29:41.800 --> 00:29:44.040
What is it?

339
00:29:46.790 --> 00:29:50.650
What kind of woman is Moo Ra?

340
00:29:50.650 --> 00:29:57.330
Did you meet with Ha Baek? Did you attack his weakest link?

341
00:29:57.330 --> 00:29:58.870
It's not like that.

342
00:29:58.870 --> 00:30:04.670
You did well. Show him how superior you are and how lacking he is here.

343
00:30:04.670 --> 00:30:09.890
- Do you mean it?
- Even if he goes, I can't just send him like this. I'm going to shrivel him up and then send him.

344
00:30:09.890 --> 00:30:15.830
No, rather than sending him all shriveled up, I'm going to burn him to a crisp and then send him.

345
00:30:15.830 --> 00:30:21.040
You gods really don't have any middle ground.

346
00:30:21.040 --> 00:30:25.000
Moo Ra is the most loyal among us. You know this too.

347
00:30:25.000 --> 00:30:28.980
- But if you turn your back on her, she's ruthless.
- Are you acting like this even though you know that about her?

348
00:30:28.980 --> 00:30:34.170
I'm an exception of course. My relationship with Moo Ra is beyond that.

349
00:30:34.170 --> 00:30:39.190
I've made a mistake coming to you. You don't know Moo Ra very well either.

350
00:30:39.190 --> 00:30:42.580
You don't know Moo Ra's true heart, right?

351
00:30:46.800 --> 00:30:48.680
I'm really no match for you.

352
00:30:48.680 --> 00:30:53.020
You don't know anything but you know everything. And you know everything but you don't know anything.

353
00:30:53.020 --> 00:30:56.370
That's the difference between you and me.

354
00:30:56.370 --> 00:31:01.720
Yes.  What you say is correct. I can't grasp it.

355
00:31:01.720 --> 00:31:05.290
I can't get a feel for how far I need to go.

356
00:31:05.290 --> 00:31:10.790
If you pay me a consultation fee, I'll give you advice.

357
00:31:14.460 --> 00:31:18.560
These merciless gods. Are they really going to act like this to the end?

358
00:31:24.290 --> 00:31:27.450
- Where are you going?
- Oh?

359
00:31:27.450 --> 00:31:29.620
I'm going to work to pay back the cancellation fee.

360
00:31:29.620 --> 00:31:32.160
I told you not to go.

361
00:31:34.530 --> 00:31:38.930
I'm sorry. He said that he would follow me here.

362
00:31:40.500 --> 00:31:43.300
He's a great worker.

363
00:31:44.880 --> 00:31:53.190
I don't know much about the gods' realm but the Ha Baek that I've heard about would never do something like that.

364
00:31:55.490 --> 00:31:58.160
There's a reason that Hye Ra is unhappy with him.

365
00:31:58.160 --> 00:32:04.520
He's saying he will pay for the breach of the contract that way. I told him I get paid the daily wage, but I can't get through to him.

366
00:32:04.520 --> 00:32:06.350
Isn't it that he doesn't understand the concept of a daily wage?

367
00:32:06.350 --> 00:32:11.890
If he didn't know about it then I could just explain it to him, but it turns out that he knew about it.

368
00:32:11.890 --> 00:32:15.630
He read about "emperor's labor". <i>(rich convicts who work to compensate for a fine, abuse the system by making even $500,000 daily in prison)</i>

369
00:32:15.630 --> 00:32:20.560
Even a human CEO makes ₩5 million ($500,000), so my labor would be priceless.

370
00:32:20.560 --> 00:32:25.900
However I'll give him the honor of putting a price on my labor. Go.

371
00:32:27.090 --> 00:32:31.790
So, what is the price he set for the labor of a king?

372
00:32:33.500 --> 00:32:38.400
- $50 million.
- Oh, $50 million?

373
00:32:38.400 --> 00:32:42.920
He said that after you deduct the cancellation fee, he'll accept the rest in cash.

374
00:32:48.660 --> 00:32:50.680
$50 million?

375
00:32:50.680 --> 00:32:54.620
You've found out the power of money, even if your strategy was a bit clumsy.

376
00:32:58.320 --> 00:33:02.720
Do you think that if Miss Yoon So Ah had plenty of money, there would be no chance for me to get involved with her?

377
00:33:02.720 --> 00:33:07.330
Regardless of whether she's rich or not, you won't have a place in her heart.

378
00:33:07.330 --> 00:33:09.790
You really don't know her.

379
00:33:09.790 --> 00:33:12.000
Is that so?

380
00:33:12.000 --> 00:33:16.970
Then I will tell you one thing that you are not aware of.

381
00:33:16.970 --> 00:33:19.420
- There is nothing I am not aware of. 
 - There is.

382
00:33:19.420 --> 00:33:22.730
Something you will never know as a god.

383
00:33:22.730 --> 00:33:26.050
Something I am able to know because I am a human.

384
00:33:27.150 --> 00:33:28.580
What?

385
00:33:29.720 --> 00:33:31.690
Human beings...

386
00:33:32.530 --> 00:33:36.840
they are lonely from the moment they are born.

387
00:33:53.020 --> 00:33:55.170
Jin Geon, what is it?

388
00:34:00.060 --> 00:34:02.130
- Someone came looking for you. 
 - Who?

389
00:34:02.130 --> 00:34:04.660
- He left something for you.
 - What?

390
00:34:04.660 --> 00:34:06.750
Please give me your hand.

391
00:34:47.960 --> 00:34:51.120
Good, well done.

392
00:35:09.540 --> 00:35:12.940
This won't be planted on that side. It was brought there by mistake.

393
00:35:12.940 --> 00:35:14.450
I will hold this.

394
00:35:14.450 --> 00:35:16.160
It's okay.

395
00:35:19.000 --> 00:35:20.770
Go.

396
00:35:20.770 --> 00:35:23.750
No, he's not a kid.

397
00:35:23.750 --> 00:35:28.350
If gods in the Water Kingdom heard that, they will be flabbergasted. A kid?

398
00:35:28.350 --> 00:35:31.610
I am really curious,

399
00:35:31.610 --> 00:35:34.680
is he someone that great?

400
00:35:34.680 --> 00:35:36.870
I don't know too well.

401
00:35:36.870 --> 00:35:40.350
My whole world consisted of the cave.

402
00:35:40.350 --> 00:35:46.890
However, of the stories about the gods' realm that Joo Geol Rin sometimes told me, half were about Ha Baek.

403
00:35:46.890 --> 00:35:50.480
Inside the cave, Ha Baek seemed like the god of gods.

404
00:35:50.480 --> 00:35:52.230
The god of gods?

405
00:35:52.230 --> 00:35:56.320
Not all gods have equal divine powers.

406
00:35:57.120 --> 00:36:00.570
What's possible for some isn't possible for others.

407
00:36:00.570 --> 00:36:04.410
However, Ha Baek is a being in which all powers are present.

408
00:36:04.410 --> 00:36:06.420
Since he was born a king.

409
00:36:06.420 --> 00:36:10.480
However, even for Ha Baek, there are two things he can't do.

410
00:36:10.480 --> 00:36:14.070
He can't revive what's dead.

411
00:36:15.960 --> 00:36:18.490
And he doesn't have the power I have.

412
00:36:19.510 --> 00:36:22.280
Still, Ha Baek is not intimidated by me in the least.

413
00:36:22.280 --> 00:36:25.980
To be honest, I liked that.

414
00:36:29.430 --> 00:36:33.670
But... are you okay?

415
00:36:34.490 --> 00:36:37.470
He might have to leave tomorrow.

416
00:36:38.910 --> 00:36:42.220
He might be gone when you wake up in the morning.

417
00:36:43.930 --> 00:36:47.470
Still, he came back

418
00:36:47.470 --> 00:36:50.140
so that I will be able to live on.

419
00:37:05.110 --> 00:37:07.240
Are you finished?

420
00:37:07.240 --> 00:37:09.090
Yes.

421
00:37:09.090 --> 00:37:12.960
$50 million, that's cheap for my labor.

422
00:37:12.960 --> 00:37:14.880
Give it to me.

423
00:37:16.140 --> 00:37:17.780
What are you doing? It doesn't suit you.

424
00:37:17.780 --> 00:37:19.740
Why not?

425
00:37:20.790 --> 00:37:25.030
You still don't get it. How I could be attractive in so many different ways.

426
00:37:25.030 --> 00:37:27.040
Should I show you?

427
00:37:27.040 --> 00:37:29.440
Don't.

428
00:37:29.440 --> 00:37:30.780
Don't do such things.

429
00:37:30.780 --> 00:37:34.060
Before your heart bursts from pounding so hard, hold on tight.

430
00:37:34.060 --> 00:37:36.390
I said don't.

431
00:37:51.240 --> 00:37:53.420
Seriously.

432
00:37:53.420 --> 00:37:55.870
I said don't.

433
00:37:56.740 --> 00:38:00.180
