437
00:38:22.240 --> 00:38:23.180
Your heart is okay?

438
00:38:23.180 --> 00:38:27.910
My heart is perfectly fine and I feel like I will become a chicken and fly away.<i> (="so cheesy I'll get goosebumps")</i>

