00:38:28.740 --> 00:38:31.560
Come this way. Take a seat.

440
00:38:42.570 --> 00:38:44.970
Why do you try to stand out like this? This isn't like you.

441
00:38:44.970 --> 00:38:49.470
Isn't it similar to how you snuck out in front of the hourse to look at me from behind?

442
00:38:49.470 --> 00:38:50.770
What?

443
00:38:51.520 --> 00:38:54.870
You said that you have to live for 40 to 50 more years.

444
00:38:55.580 --> 00:39:00.380
Things being like that,

445
00:39:01.170 --> 00:39:04.240
you need to have more memories of me to last you till then.

446
00:39:06.770 --> 00:39:10.020
You're so good at saying such things in an indifferent way.

447
00:39:14.980 --> 00:39:18.090
I am not saying this because I am an indifferent person.

448
00:39:34.920 --> 00:39:38.260
You know that I am selfish.

449
00:39:39.820 --> 00:39:43.180
I am saying this because I am selfish.

450
00:39:44.030 --> 00:39:46.650
As much as possible,

451
00:39:47.940 --> 00:39:50.820
for a long long time,

452
00:39:52.550 --> 00:39:55.530
don't be

453
00:40:04.170 --> 00:40:07.310
I will

454
00:40:08.940 --> 00:40:13.230
remember you for a long long time.

455
00:40:37.840 --> 00:40:41.210
Are you angry because your daily wage wasn't $50 million?

456
00:40:43.730 --> 00:40:48.450
He said since you're an emperor, he will give you $5,000 for a daily wage. So go work there everyday.

457
00:40:48.450 --> 00:40:52.150
If you just work for 10 days, it will be more than enough to pay for the breach of the contract.

458
00:40:52.150 --> 00:40:55.000
If we both earn money....

459
00:40:55.840 --> 00:40:59.710
That's a funny thing to say. If we both earn money.

460
00:41:02.650 --> 00:41:07.570
We will go tomorrow and the day after...

461
00:41:08.870 --> 00:41:12.150
Let's go there together every day.

462
00:41:14.010 --> 00:41:16.740
Let's work together.

463
00:41:20.240 --> 00:41:22.840
Let's stay together.

464
00:41:24.680 --> 00:41:27.020
Okay.

